Highlights of this release

 o Don't rely on libsexy headers (Michael Biebl)

Requirements for PolicyKit-mate 0.9.2

 - PolicyKit        == 0.9
 - GTK+             >= 2.13.6
 - dbus             >= 1.0
 - dbus-glib        >= 0.71
 - MateConf            >= 2.8

